com.pb.sawdust.tabledata.basic

Class WrappedDataRow

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pb.sawdust.tabledata.basic.WrappedDataRow
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataRow
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DegenerateContextDataRow

    public class WrappedDataRow
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataRow
    The WrappedDataRow class provides a DataRow implementation which wraps another data row. All methods just (by default) pass through to the wrapped data row. This class is useful as a starting class for indirect DataRow extensions which need to only modify select behavior from the source class.
